## 2. Technical Overview

### Authentication Model
- **Method**: Bearer Token (JWT)
- **Storage**: `flutter_secure_storage`
- **API Base**: `/api/` (public) and `/api/guide/*` (authenticated)
- **Guest Sessions**: Optional support via `guest_token`
- **Push Notifications**: Device registration required (`POST /api/guide/device`)
- **Email Verification**: Required to unlock full functionality

### API Communication
- RESTful JSON
- All responses expected in standard format
- Proper error handling and token refresh mechanism required

