## 3. Detailed Features Specification

### 3.1 Authentication & Account Management
- **Registration**: Name, Email, Password, Password Confirmation, Optional Device Name & Guest Token
- **Login**: Email + Password (returns token + `converted_from_guest_session` flag)
- **Password Recovery**: Forgot → Reset flow
- **Email Verification**: Mandatory (signed URL)
- **Account Deletion**: With optional reason note + confirmation

### 3.2 Guide Profile Management
**View Profile Fields**:
- Full Name, Profile Photo, Country & City, Languages (`["en", "ar"]`), Specializations, Years of Experience, Bio, Rating, Profile Completeness %

**Editable Fields** (PATCH `/api/guide/profile`):
- full_name, country, city, languages, specializations, years_of_experience, bio

**Features**:
- Profile photo upload (Multipart, max 2MB, JPEG/PNG)
- Completeness progress bar (strongly encouraged)

### 3.3 Identity Verification (Mandatory One-time)
**Submit Fields**:
- Passport Number
- National ID
- Guide License Number
- Document URLs (array)

**Statuses**:
- `PENDING` → Yellow badge
- `VERIFIED` → Green badge
- `REJECTED` → Red badge (with resubmit)

### 3.4 Applications & Subscriptions (Marketplace)
- Browse all available apps with plans & pricing
- Filter / Search capability
- Subscribe via `POST /api/guide/subscriptions` with `plan_id`
- Support for promo codes
- Manage active and past subscriptions

### 3.5 Financial Management
- **Wallet**: Current balance + paginated transaction history
- **Commissions**: Earnings from promo code redemptions
- **Payout Requests**: Amount + Payment Method (validate ≤ balance)
- **Referral System**: Generate unique code/link, track referred users & performance

### 3.6 Promo Code System (Thoth Guide AI)
- Validate: `POST /api/thoth-guide/promo-codes/validate`
- Redeem: `POST /api/thoth-guide/promo-codes/redeem`

### 3.7 Support & Communication
- Create Ticket (Category, Priority, Subject, Message)
- Ticket List with status
- Ticket Detail + Reply thread
- Categories: PAYMENT, TECHNICAL, GENERAL, etc.
- Priorities: NORMAL, HIGH, URGENT

### 3.8 Additional Modules
- **Notifications**: Paginated list, mark as read, unread badge on tab
- **Announcements**: Time-based active announcements (prominent display)
- **Knowledge Center**: Articles by category or app_id
- **Legal Agreements**: Fetch pending → Force acceptance before gated features
- **Usage Analytics**: Silent event reporting (`POST /api/guide/analytics/event`)

