## 4. Core User Flows

### Onboarding Flow
1. Register / Login
2. Email Verification
3. Complete Profile (with completeness indicator)
4. Submit Identity Verification

### Subscription Flow
1. Browse Marketplace → Filter/Search
2. View App Details & Plans
3. Select Plan → Subscribe (with optional promo)
4. Access unlocked features

### Earnings Flow
1. Earn via referrals & promo redemptions
2. View Wallet & Transactions
3. Request Payout

### Support Flow
1. Create Ticket
2. Receive notifications on replies
3. Reply in thread

